	.------------------------------------------------------------------------.
	|  Q  |  W  |  E  |  R  |  T  |          |  Y    |  U  |  I  |  O  |  P  |
	|  A  |  S  |  D  |  F  |  G  |          |  H    |  J  |  K  |  L  |  ;  |
	|  Z  |  X  |  C  |  V  |  B* |          |  N    |  M  |  ,  |  .  |  /  |
	'-----------------\ nav | SFT |          | Sp/nm | ENT /-----------------'
	                   '----------------------------------'
