	.------------------------------------------------------------------------.
	|     |     |     |     |     |          |       |     |     |     |     |
	|lgui |lalt |lctl |lsft |     |          |       |rsft |rctl |ralt |rgui |
	|     |     |     |     |     |          |       |     |     |     |     |
	'-----------------\ nav | SFT |          | Sp/nm | ENT /-----------------'
	                   '----------------------------------'

