	                   '----------------------------------'

Navigation
	.------------------------------------------------------------------------.
	| F1  | F2  | F3  | F4  |     |          |       | ← ← |  ↑  | → → | ScS |
	| F5  | F6  | F7  | F8  |     |          |       |  ←  |  ↓  |  →  |     |
	| F9  | F10 | F11 | F12 |     |          | MPR   | MPP | MNX | MVU | MVD |
	'-----------------\ nav | SFT |          | Sp/nm | ENT /-----------------'
